      <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; color: #000000; margin-bottom: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase;">Methodological Best Practices</h3>
      <ul style="margin-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 2; color: #000000;">
        <li>Use multiple methods to assess self-esteem (triangulation)</li>
        <li>Demonstrate measurement invariance in cross-cultural research</li>
        <li>Employ longitudinal designs to examine causal hypotheses</li>
        <li>Control for common method variance in cross-sectional studies</li>
        <li>Report effect sizes alongside statistical significance</li>
        <li>Consider both between-person and within-person processes</li>
      </ul>
